23
00:01:29,860 --> 00:01:32,000
Humans were originally hunter-gatherers.

24
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:36,200
They scavenged for food and often didn't live in a set place, similar to how animals

25
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:40,460
live, but then in 10,000 BC we learned to farm.

26
00:01:40,460 --> 00:01:45,440
The domestication of plants allowed humans to finally settle down in one singular place

27
00:01:45,440 --> 00:01:50,260
and establish a long-term home, but farming was nothing like it is today.

28
00:01:50,260 --> 00:01:53,760
The humans of the era lacked technology and expertise.

29
00:01:53,760 --> 00:01:58,140
